      "content": "Yeah, I'll check the load balancer and the connection pooling. But it's still really driving me crazy because it feels so... unexplainable. One minute everything is perfect, and the next, a handful of requests just fall into a black hole for no reason. It's like there's some invisible force just messing with the connections. \n\nIs there any way we can set up more granular tracing to see exactly where the request \"disappears\" in the stack? I want to catch it in the act.",
